  Pin        string `mapstructure:"pin" json:"pin"`                                                                        
  SoftVerify bool   `mapstructure:"softwareverify,omitempty" json:"softwareverify,omitempty"`                              
  Immutable  bool   `mapstructure:"immutable,omitempty" json:"immutable,omitempty"`                                        
} 
{code}

From what I can tell, the examples in the documentation should be quoting the pin.

The SecLevel field (named âsecurityâ in the configuration document) is a different story. If setting the environment variable causes a problem, thatâs a bug in the code that needs to be addressed.

